hopobject.body: It's a bad line galaxy pharma karachi address You need to understand it is a carefully crafted argument to distract you from what the wealthy class will be doing to other areas of the tax code, such as income from investment — which is where the wealthy get most of their income (i.e. passive investment, not income from wages) — and which they intend to drop down to the present 15% for capital gains, which would cut their taxes for investment income literally in half.
